gie）</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- 在 All Things Open 现场录制，Robbie 和 Nick Taylor 与 Brian Douglas（Bdougie）探讨开源对职业的影响、OpenSauced 的兴衰，以及为什么开发者工具会成功或失败。他们深入讨论了 Git 哲学、编辑器战争、AI 对编码的混乱影响，以及像 Rails 这样的强大框架如何继续塑造生态系统。还聊到了 TypeScript 代理、AI 编码工具的未来，以及如何评估 AI 生成的内容。</span></p>\n  <div style=\"padding:16px 20px;text-size-adjust:auto;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.476px;display:flex;font-size:12px;border-color:rgb(62, 62, 62);box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;border-radius:6px;box-shadow:rgb(199, 201, 204) 0px 0px 0px inset;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;margin-top:12px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;align-items:center;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;\">\n   <div style=\"margin: 0 !important;padding-right: 12px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;flex: 1 1 0%;display: flex;flex-direction: column;justify-content: space-between;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <strong style=\"font-size: 12px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(114, 114, 114);line-height: 1.75em;font-weight: bold;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span leaf=\"\">长按识别二维码查看原文</span></strong>\n    <p style=\"padding-top: 8px;padding-bottom: 8px;margin: 0;font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Segoe UI', Arial, freesans,\n    sans-serif;text-align: start;white-space: normal;text-size-adjust: auto;font-size: 12px;margin-bottom: 0;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;min-height: 1em;line-height: 1.8;color: rgb(114, 114, 114);word-break: break-all;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://play.cdnstream1.com/s/radicalcompany/whiskey-web-and-whatnot-bda353/are-developers-overthink-b2a01f\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.cdnstream1.com/s/radicalcompany/whiskey-web-and-whatnot-bda353/are-developers-overthink-b2a01f</a></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"display: flex;align-items: center;max-width: 90px;box-sizing: border-box;flex-shrink: 0;font-size: 0px;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100061366\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"212\" style=\"margin: 0 auto;max-width: 100%;margin-right: auto;margin-left: auto;box-sizing: border-box;vertical-align: middle;border-style: none;display: block;border-radius: 4px;overflow-wrap: break-word;visibility: visible;width: 90px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d1fab8af&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FINNfEriciaG5dvxVKUibFHtBAHA8WgAO3oFP51bVI2uyjIsktQk3ouEGB7VibW0AJsDuA3OgCaARP4MDibS38unvvicQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"padding-top:8px;margin:0;text-size-adjust:auto;white-space:normal;padding-bottom:8px;font-size:15px;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Segoe UI', Arial, freesans,\n    sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;box-sizing:border-box;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:start;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;word-wrap: break-word;font-weight: bold;color: rgb(239, 112, 96);\"><span leaf=\"\">ShopTalk：693 - 爱好、拼图游戏电路和 Web 货币化新闻</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- 从感恩节大餐的选择聊起，讨论我们真正需要多少爱好、为什么不能全部完成，Clues by Sam 的难度和拼图游戏电路，Dave 是否喜欢 D&amp;D 还是喜欢系统，以及正在进行的 Web 货币化尝试。节目还探讨了 Brecht on range group 和 Web Monetization 的最新进展。</span></p>\n  <div style=\"padding:16px 20px;text-size-adjust:auto;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.476px;display:flex;font-size:12px;border-color:rgb(62, 62, 62);box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;border-radius:6px;box-shadow:rgb(199, 201, 204) 0px 0px 0px inset;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;margin-top:12px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;align-items:center;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;\">\n   <div style=\"margin: 0 !important;paddin